taylorr	vrpn_Tracker.C ( ), vrpn_Tracker.h ( )
Modified the packing code to use vrpn_buffer() and vrpn_unbufer().
Removed the redundant change handlers for all sensors, by replacing them with
ones that have optional parameters.

